Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:09.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早晨的散步也别有风味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哟～呵～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.74,0:00:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事件结束后没多久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,3年A班的学生们回到了现实世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:21.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重新过起了安稳的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…再睡就又要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:28.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再睡5分…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才你就已经说过再睡5分钟了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再睡10分…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,延长时间怎么成啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  我赶来接您了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:45.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜  快起床
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.39,0:00:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再睡15分…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又延长了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下手完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.69,0:01:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…小刹毫不手软呐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真平静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.81,0:01:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时拯救了我们的光芒…莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.63,0:01:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「就此圆满告终！？」by 旁白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是星水晶事件的始末
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…请问…学园长…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于阿妮亚的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来嘛～是应该遭受重罚的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里  现在一切圆满  不如就这样算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会想办法与魔法学校那边交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.55,0:03:33.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然学园长这么说  我们也没有什么异议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将此事也当作修行的一环即可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管对涅吉来说是一场异常艰苦的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是被迫变成卓柏卡布拉  似乎过于难为他了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是作为魔法学校的特使尽忠职守
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,汇报了涅吉同学的不幸的事而已  没有恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:03:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们是冒牌的特使喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让你泄密的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早就人尽皆知了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.13,0:04:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  现在开始进行复习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉的事  从涅佳涅姐姐这边听说的时候简直难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直怀疑涅吉是不是因为进展不顺而偷偷地哭鼻子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  接下来可以麻烦五月同学朗读一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,五月同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,五月同学也会打瞌睡可真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确很稀奇呀  这回可是连明日菜都还没睡着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,睡着了呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  通宵思索着今天派对的菜谱就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:05:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么相应地  今天的丰盛大餐就全拜托这位小妹啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:03.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要举办派对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  还没有告诉阿妮亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:09.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家说好了一起举办庆祝会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.79,0:05:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,参加此类活动似乎也不错…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚妹妹也请务必参加哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  今天的课程到此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快  回去进行派对的准备！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah～派对  要狂欢咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  会狂欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟平安地从魔法世界回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.25,0:05:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是不该提起「魔法世界」的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…  怎么办  我说错话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚妹妹还在为此次事件而内疚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:00.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找阿妮亚谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家先开始准备起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,班长同学  接下来就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  涅吉  我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也陪同前往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.06,0:06:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就请包在我身上  涅吉老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会将派对办得有声有色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都听明白了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！  在那！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:27.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！  阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站住啊  我有话和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,lilios
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…「木叶遁」？  伊贺流忍术吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔法啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜  这就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完美！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.38,0:07:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小夜同学  这能够得着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完成～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是么  那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,盯～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.84,0:07:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～会飞真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两位只要变成幽灵也同样会飞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  又一个完成～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美砂好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事包在我身上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失败～又撕坏了～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,樱子就很笨拙了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.98,0:07:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那小圆你自己又如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有两下子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶  究竟是谁做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正折  反折…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再假装正折实则反折…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是专家喵  没有恶意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是只青蛙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为是青蛙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家  有没有浏览千羽千羽的漂流日记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:30.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心潮澎湃激动人心的魔法世界大冒险充满惊险天马行空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看一眼便会无法自拔哟～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！  浏览数增加  Good Job！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是本天才
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来来来…看看有什么反响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:42.10,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1385,540)\an4\fs35\bord2\blur1\b0}322 ：C. N.：无名氏:2007/3/20(火)\N\h\h\h电波系来啦—！\N323 ：电波MM来啦—————！\N324 ：不不…与其说是「电波系」、\N\h\h\h感觉更像是真正的「电波」啊…\N325：电波信号开始接受！\N326 ：千羽千羽～\N327 ：阻止\N328 ：但我拒绝\N329 ：这电波系可真不错呢\N330 ：什么嘛  电波什么的无关紧要！\N\h\h\h胸部！上传胸部啊！\N331 ：但我拒绝\N332 ：如果30分钟内有人回复的话、\N\h\h\h电波MM就是我的了！\N333 ：肚子饿了、聊聊咖喱的话题吧？\N334 ：阻止\N335 ：千雨的话、现在就睡在我身边，\N\h\h\h有意见吗？\N336 ：你别妄想啦\N337 ：阻止\N338 ：阻止\N339 ：我觉得做咖喱不将土豆这素材\N\h\h\h煮烂是基本。\N340 ：>>335  看仔细了。那只是腐女啦。\N\h\h\h不够电波啦你难道不懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是电波系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也得说成「不可思议少女」！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～「不可思议少女」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卷心菜  番茄  四季豆  洋葱  生菜和胡萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就集齐了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.59,0:09:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,晶  五月的笔记呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩下青椒…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有青椒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！  对了！  撒下种子试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后很快就会生长出来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是身处魔法世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:18.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,轰轰轰轰轰轰轰轰轰轰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们自以为胜券在握了  去给他们点颜色看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是那边还是这边  总归存在着一成不变的事物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.84,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,轰轰轰轰轰轰轰轰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:25.37,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,轰轰轰轰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被洼地给绊住了前行的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:31.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔女老太婆的诅咒么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,裕奈别玩了  快来帮忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.42,0:09:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Sir！ Yes Sir！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莳绘同学  能否赶快将盘子给摆放好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,餐叉在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部放在这个碗橱里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果汁准备得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.45,0:09:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  班长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莳绘同学  为什么今天反常地伶俐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！？  不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就应该犯错  然后被我指责「失去资格！」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正的佐佐木莳绘！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法失去资格的佐佐木莳绘作为佐佐木莳绘失去资格！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说有些莫名…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.11,0:10:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…打击～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是乱来呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.12,0:10:14.12,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（街头）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  阿妮亚  听我们说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.11,0:10:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,lilios
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真下得了手  看我不捉住你好好调教一番
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.73,0:10:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明日菜  转变初衷可不成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「友好相处甚是和谐哉」by 学园长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请  大家各自去分配吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吸血鬼的魔法药吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.41,0:10:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是主人之前设法制造药物使自己成长时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,调试失败的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说这些都是次品？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  失败后却生成了恢复青春药
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恢复青春药！？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言没有任何价值  就送给你们了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喝了它就会变得年轻吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  年龄不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那究竟是什么东西恢复青春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,皮肤的年龄！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！  皮肤还能恢复青春？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这真让人感兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想要！  给我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:40.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要喝～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～皮肤光滑无比
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,细嫩得犹如婴儿一般呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,简直晶莹剔透
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有了它  不用再害怕什么紫外线了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害！  太厉害了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是女人的致命武器啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这结果还真是有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这药物中包含着…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.47,0:12:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脊索动物门两栖纲山椒鱼目(即有尾目)的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,光滑啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.12,0:12:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…是赤腹蝾螈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:22.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以及…脊椎动物亚门哺乳纲翼手目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.11,0:12:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…蝙蝠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.32,0:12:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:35.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…软体动物门腹足纲有肺亚纲柄眼目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…是蛞蝓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.01,0:12:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶～～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来来  「要不然我也奉陪一下」差不多这样如何啊  那么就～呵呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,据说里面也加入过青蛙喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,的确有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙真烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  千鹤姐  派对的礼物送什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就决定好咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇…好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.63,0:13:09.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打算将这丝带作为礼物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,答·错·了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好～  完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗～？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密礼物  该咋办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,13分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最近评分是不是过于严格了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人会成长嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你成长了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…  4分…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…100万分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特意为今天的派对做了史无前例的珍藏版铃音风肉包子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶～是怎样的肉包子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.38,0:13:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尝试添加了铃音心目中世界第一美味的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.17,0:13:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铃音心目中世界第一美味的食物…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:13:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,铛～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起世界上最美味的食物——肉包子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:07.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是它！  究极的肉包子——肉包子馅的肉包子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,里面的肉包子又是什么馅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然还是肉包子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那还算肉包子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家品尝等级提升后的世界珍味面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,茶茶丸  解决他！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟丢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟跑哪儿去了呢  阿妮亚妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过的确看她跑到这附近来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎感觉到了什么的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…魔杖却没什么反应
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉  卧倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是…暗影！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,lilios
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.02,0:15:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  都叫你别跟来了  你却不理会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会有暗影…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,星水晶早就被封印了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还残留着被释放出来的暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没有那方面的反应啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…被星水晶占据过的我清楚得很
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:24.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不告诉我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们多少也可以帮上忙才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这事必须由我亲手了结
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩一个就全部结束了  别来妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.84,0:15:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！？  怎…怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.52,0:15:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是个死小鬼还无谓地逞什么能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:50.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.96,0:15:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  和涅吉一样还是个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只会逞能  以为什么事都能自己解决
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也来帮忙  明白了么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…不能再给你们添麻烦了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么见外的话啊  我们不是朋友嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错啊  阿妮亚妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友呢  就是互相添麻烦互相帮助的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有这么个大家伙残留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暗影的中心在…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼疼…腰闪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…刚才好险…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:05.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们自愿说要帮忙的  被抓住也怨不得他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.17,0:17:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了  阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.79,0:17:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  接下来轮到我们表现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我们变身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,神乐坂明日菜  近卫木乃香  樱咲刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向我展现出来吧 那隐藏着的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,契约发动！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.08,0:17:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全是Cosplay Card啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:17:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚  该瞄准哪里才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:17:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了  我们会杀出一条路来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿妮亚  上来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,秘剑  五谷丰饶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在  阿妮亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,de clio lilios
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也饿得肚子咕咕叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,推开门扉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别问了  赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:16.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到麻帆良学园女子中学部3年A班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:20.65,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎…  欢迎…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.77,0:19:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这位便是今天的主角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主角应该表现得大大方方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,主角？  今天不是庆祝大家平安回归…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…骗你的～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想给你个惊喜所以一直保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是举办欢迎阿妮亚的派对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为我举办？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为阿妮亚妹妹回来后就一直无精打采
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就想到了大家一起狂欢一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞒着你真对不起啊
